snippet.title: Mortal Kombat 1 - Official Quan Chi Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
The power of the NetherRealm is at his fingertips. Beware his sorcery. Quan Chi arrives in #MK1 for Early Access on December 14, Full Release December 21. Khameleon joins the kameo roster in January.

Get the Premium Edition or add the Kombat Pack to your Standard Edition to play as Quan Chi: https://www.mortalkombat.com/purchase

It's In Our Blood. Discover a reborn Mortal Kombat Universe created by Fire God Liu Kang. Mortal Kombat 1 ushers in a new era of the iconic franchise with a new fighting system, game modes, and Fatalities!
